### Assign PCP
POST http://localhost:8081/api/patients/{{patientId}}/primary-care
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hospitalId": "{{hospitalId}}",
  "assignmentId": "{{doctorAssignmentId}}",
  "startDate": "2025-08-10",
  "notes": "Initial PCP"
}

### Get current PCP
GET http://localhost:8081/api/patients/{{patientId}}/primary-care/current
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### History
GET http://localhost:8081/api/patients/{{patientId}}/primary-care/history
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Update PCP
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/primary-care/{{pcpId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endDate": "2025-12-31",
  "notes": "Updated note"
}

### End PCP
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/primary-care/{{pcpId}}/end?endDate=2025-10-01
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Delete PCP
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/primary-care/{{pcpId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
